---
title: Tofu Korma-Style Curry with Rice and Garlic Flatbread
description: Aromatics and spices come together perfectly in this velvety, cashew-based tofu curry. Add a fluffy bed of rice and garlicky flatbread and your stomach is going to be smiling!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cari-de-tofu-facon-korma-c98482b0.jpg
